# Template Extensions

When it comes to creating text documents, like
[custom_templates](../guide.md#custom-templates) or exporting tests, plans
and stories into ReST or Markdown, tmt relies on the well-known
[Jinja](https://palletsprojects.com/p/jinja/) package. All Jinja templating features are supported, and, on
top of [filters](https://jinja.palletsprojects.com/en/3.1.x/templates/#filters) and [tests](https://jinja.palletsprojects.com/en/stable/templates/#tests) shipped with Jinja, tmt adds several
custom ones.

